      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS POLLYWOOD (1) jumps from the inside draw. Latest effort finished 4th on May 5 over 450m at this track behind Most Determined beaten 6 lengths (25.77) in a Grade 4/5. Suited here and can find winning form. ULTIMATE ETHICS (4) missed the frame last time when fourth (31.96) at Maitland but prior to that had three placings in a row. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Can measure up this time. SNOOPY'S ETHICS (2) is having his first start around this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 5.5 lengths (30.57) at Wentworth Park. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. PAW FORTRESS (5) comes into calculations after placing in a quick run most recently.",
